-- Arcelik to Build Region's Biggest Appliance Unit in Egypt, Milliyet Says
-- Mark Bentley
-- 2010-06-22T05:59:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/arcelik-to-build-region-s-biggest-appliance-unit-in-egypt-milliyet-says.html

          
          
             Arcelik AS , Turkey’s largest maker 
of fridges and washing machines, will build the Middle East’s 
biggest home appliance factory in Egypt, Milliyet reported.  
 Turk Sise & Cam Fabrikalari AS , a glassmaker, is also in 
talks to build a factory in the country, the Istanbul-based 
newspaper said citing Huseyin Avni Botsali, Turkey’s ambassador
to Egypt.  
